I got kicked out of school for Fighting. I think everyone really knows the story or has heard about it.Well it has been 5 days and back to school I get to go 2morrow I am so VERY HAPPY.Well when I was out of school my mom or sister took me shopping so it was pretty good to be out of school.The thing that sucked was the homework I had to make up.I also was not able to talk to my freinds even tho I always find ways around it lmao.My grandma came up from Alabama so it was nice spending sometime with her sense I never see her.Being locked up in ur house for 5days not counting the weekend sucks.Kyle,Joey & me went up to apple charlies.That was my 1st time out of the house with my friends.Think twice before your going to fight but if u know you are going to win then kick there ASS.

Thats all for now...:)Word of the night "fucka fuck"
